ssdp(Simple Service Discovery Protocol) åè®®åŸæ–‡å¯ä»¥æŸ¥çœ‹ [https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-cai-ssdp-v1-00](https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-cai-ssdp-v1-00)

